          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Illinois child care licensing — Code 385 (Background Checks) and each person's complete, signed authorization to conduct the background check; 8) Effective January 1, 2014, as part of an initial application, the Department shall require proof the center has been tested within the last 3 years for radon by a Radon Measurement Professional licensed by the Illinois Emergency Management Agency (see 32 Ill.",
