          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Illinois child care licensing — 65 Provisions Pertaining to Permits a) A permit shall not be issued prior to the following: 1) Completion of the application for license and submission to the Department; 2) Employment of a child care director who has passed the background check requirements of 89 Ill.",
